		<br />
	</div> containing the MB90082.BIN file for use in no$sns BIOS folder (works with the currently released no$sns version) (ie. no$sns v1.4 was ready to support the font once when it gets dumped) (though the emulator's font resizing doesn't look too well, maybe I'll add some cosmetic fixes on that part in next no$sns versions).</div>

